              @click.prevent="changeTab('chat-gpt-assistant')"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="w-6 h-6 stroke-red-500"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="font-medium">Chat GPT Assistant</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <button
          class="lg:hidden w-6 bg-gray-50 border-l border-b border-gray-100 text-gray-600 disabled:text-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center"
          :disabled="scrolledRight"
          @click="scrollRight"
          disabled="disabled"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            fill="currentColor"
            class="w-5 h-5"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M7.21 14.77a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06L11.168 10 7.23 6.29a.75.75 0 111.04-1.08l4.5 4.25a.75.75 0 010 1.08l-4.5 4.25a.75.75 0 01-1.06-.02z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </nav>

      <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto">
        <div x-init="tabs.push('list-building')"></div>

        <div class="p-5 md:p-8 lg:px-12" x-show="tab === 'list-building'">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">List Building</h3>
          <div
            class="mt-4 leading-relaxed [&_pre]:bg-[#161414] [&_pre_code.torchlight]:!bg-[#161414] [&_pre]:leading-8 [&_pre]:p-2 [&_a]:text-red-600 [&_a]:underline hover:[&_a]:no-underline [&_strong]:font-medium [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:ml-4 space-y-4"
          >
            <p>
              List Building adalah proses mengumpulkan kontak (biasanya berupa
              alamat email atau nomor telepon) dari calon pelanggan atau
              pelanggan yang sudah ada. Tujuannya adalah untuk terus
              berkomunikasi, memberikan informasi, dan menawarkan produk atau
              layanan kepada mereka.
            </p>
            <!-- @ts-ignore:next-line -->
            <Image src={ListBuilding} alt="Image" format="avif" />
            <p>
              Gunakan Dripsender BOT untuk menyimpan Kontak secara Otomatis ke
              dalam List ketika ada calon pelanggan menghubungi anda.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div x-init="tabs.push('evergreen-campaign')"></div>

        <div
          class="p-5 md:p-8 lg:px-12"
          x-show="tab === 'evergreen-campaign'"
          style="display: none;"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">Evergreen Campaign</h3>
          <div
            class="mt-4 leading-relaxed [&_pre]:bg-[#161414] [&_pre_code.torchlight]:!bg-[#161414] [&_pre]:leading-8 [&_pre]:p-2 [&_a]:text-red-600 [&_a]:underline hover:[&_a]:no-underline [&_strong]:font-medium [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:ml-4 space-y-4"
          >
            <p>
              Dengan Evergreen Campaign anda bisa mengotomasi proses Follow up
              setelah List Building. Setelah Lead masuk ke dalam List anda, anda
              bisa mengirimkan serial pesan sampai CLOSING.
            </p>
            <!-- @ts-ignore:next-line -->
            <Image src={EvergreenCampaign} alt="Image" format="avif" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div x-init="tabs.push('bot-automation')"></div>

        <div
          class="p-5 md:p-8 lg:px-12"
          x-show="tab === 'bot-automation'"
          style="display: none;"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">Automation with BOT</h3>
          <div
            class="mt-4 leading-relaxed [&_pre]:bg-[#161414] [&_pre_code.torchlight]:!bg-[#161414] [&_pre]:leading-8 [&_pre]:p-2 [&_a]:text-red-600 [&_a]:underline hover:[&_a]:no-underline [&_strong]:font-medium [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:ml-4 space-y-4"
          >
            <p>
              Dripsender BOT akan membaca semua pesan yang masuk. Jika ada
              Keyword yang sesuai dengan text pesan, maka secara OTOMATIS akan
              mentrigger Action yang anda set.
            </p>
            <!-- @ts-ignore:next-line -->
            <Image src={DripsenderBot} alt="Image" format="avif" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div x-init="tabs.push('campaign-with-ai')"></div>

        <div
          class="p-5 md:p-8 lg:px-12"
          x-show="tab === 'campaign-with-ai'"
          style="display: none;"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">Campaign with AI</h3>
          <div
            class="mt-4 leading-relaxed [&_pre]:bg-[#161414] [&_pre_code.torchlight]:!bg-[#161414] [&_pre]:leading-8 [&_pre]:p-2 [&_a]:text-red-600 [&_a]:underline hover:[&_a]:no-underline [&_strong]:font-medium [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:ml-4 space-y-4"
          >
            <p>Gak Jago Nulis, Tapi Mau buat tulisan menghipnotis?</p>
            <p>
              Tidak perlu lagi menjadi seorang ahli dalam menulis, karena kami
              telah menggabungkan teknologi AI terdepan dengan kreativitasmu.
              Sekarang, dengan mudahnya, Anda bisa membuat kata-kata yang
              menggugah, penuh daya tarik, dan menjual tanpa perlu repot-repot
              memikirkan setiap kata yang harus ditulis.
            </p>
            <p>Begini caranya:</p>
            <p>
              1. Cukup tuliskan sedikit informasi tentang produk atau
              kampanyemu.
            </p>
            <p>
              2. Kemudian, berikan panduan singkat tentang gaya, nada, dan pesan
              yang ingin Anda sampaikan.
            </p>
            <p>
              3. Biarkan AI kami mengambil alih dan menghasilkan teks yang luar
              biasa sesuai dengan panduanmu!
            </p>
            <p>
              Tunggu apa lagi? Segera coba layanan kami yang revolusioner ini
              dan rasakan sendiri bagaimana AI dapat membantu Anda menghadirkan
              kata-kata yang mendalam dan mengesankan.
            </p>
            <p>Hemat waktu, tenaga, dan pastinya pikiranmu!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div x-init="tabs.push('chat-gpt-assistant')"></div>

        <div
          class="p-5 md:p-8 lg:px-12"
          x-show="tab === 'chat-gpt-assistant'"
          style="display: none;"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">CHAT GPT Assistant</h3>
          <div
            class="mt-4 leading-relaxed [&_pre]:bg-[#161414] [&_pre_code.torchlight]:!bg-[#161414] [&_pre]:leading-8 [&_pre]:p-2 [&_a]:text-red-600 [&_a]:underline hover:[&_a]:no-underline [&_strong]:font-medium [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:ml-4 space-y-4"
          >
            <p>
             Integrasikan Whatsapp Anda dengan Chat GPT Assistant. Dengan Mengubah Whatsapp Anda menjadi CHAT GPT, Anda bisa mengotomasi semua pesan yang masuk ke dalam Whatsapp Anda.
            </p>
            <p>Selanjutnya AI yang akan memberikan balasan kepada semua pertanyaan yang masuk.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div x-init="tabs.push('notifications')"></div>

        <div
          class="p-5 md:p-8 lg:px-12"
          x-show="tab === 'notifications'"
          style="display: none;"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">Notifications &amp; Mail</h3>
          <div
            class="mt-4 leading-relaxed [&_pre]:bg-[#161414] [&_pre_code.torchlight]:!bg-[#161414] [&_pre]:leading-8 [&_pre]:p-2 [&_a]:text-red-600 [&_a]:underline hover:[&_a]:no-underline [&_strong]:font-medium [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:ml-4 space-y-4"
          >
            <p>
              Use Laravel to quickly send beautifully styled notifications to
              your users via email, Slack, SMS, in-app, and more:
            </p>

            <pre><code data-theme="olaolu-palenight" data-lang="bash" class="torchlight" style="background-color: #292D3E; --theme-selection-background: #7580B850;"><!-- Syntax highlighted by torchlight.dev --><div class="line"><span style="color: #BFC7D5;">php </span><span style="color: #BFC7D5;">artisan</span><span style="color: #BFC7D5;"> </span><span style="color: #BFC7D5;">make:notification</span><span style="color: #BFC7D5;"> </span><span style="color: #BFC7D5;">InvoicePaid</span></div></code></pre>

            <p>
              Once you have generated a notification, you can easily send the
              message to one of your application's users:
            </p>

            <pre><code data-theme="olaolu-palenight" data-lang="php" class="torchlight" style="background-color: #292D3E; --theme-selection-background: #7580B850;"><!-- Syntax highlighted by torchlight.dev --><div class="line"><span style="color: #BEC5D4;">$user</span><span style="color: #89DDFF;">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #82AAFF;">notify</span><span style="color: #BFC7D5;">(</span><span style="color: #89DDFF;">new</span><span style="color: #BFC7D5;"> </span><span style="color: #FFCB8B;">InvoicePaid</span><span style="color: #BFC7D5;">(</span><span style="color: #BEC5D4;">$invoice</span><span style="color: #BFC7D5;">));</span></div></code></pre>

            <p>
              <a href="https://laravel.com/docs/notifications">Learn more</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div x-init="tabs.push('storage')"></div>

        <div
          class="p-5 md:p-8 lg:px-12"
          x-show="tab === 'storage'"
          style="display: none;"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">File Storage</h3>
          <div
            class="mt-4 leading-relaxed [&_pre]:bg-[#161414] [&_pre_code.torchlight]:!bg-[#161414] [&_pre]:leading-8 [&_pre]:p-2 [&_a]:text-red-600 [&_a]:underline hover:[&_a]:no-underline [&_strong]:font-medium [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:ml-4 space-y-4"
          >
            <p>
              Laravel provides a robust filesystem abstraction layer, providing
              a single, unified API for interacting with local filesystems and
              cloud based filesystems like Amazon S3:
